        <Str Cat="Text">
          <Val><![CDATA[If your application is connecting to an AlwaysOn availability group (AG) on different subnets, setting this to true provides faster detection of and connection to the (currently) active server.]]></Val>
          <Tgt Cat="Text" Stat="Loc" Orig="New">
